'''《极速前进26》'''（{{lang|en|'''''The Amazing Race 26'''''}}），是[[哥倫比亞廣播公司|CBS]]的流行[[真人秀|真人競賽節目]]《[[极速前进美国版|极速前进]]》的第二十六季。本季与以往各季不同，十一支参赛队伍全部为正在约会的情侣关系，其中五支队伍中是在比赛前刚刚通过节目相亲结识的，另外六支队伍则是已经约会了一段时间的情侣。十一支队伍為最終大獎——一百萬[[美元|美元]]進行環球旅行競賽。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thewrap.com/the-amazing-race-has-a-new-twist-blind-date-couples/ |title=‘The Amazing Race’ Has a New Twist: Blind Date Couples |last1=Glazer |first1=Mikey |date=2014-12-19 |publisher=The Wrap |accessdate=2015-04-05 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125030213/https://www.thewrap.com/the-amazing-race-has-a-new-twist-blind-date-couples/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.realityblurred.com/realitytv/2014/12/amazing-race-blind-date-major-change/ |title=Amazing Race drops pre-existing relationships for blind date twist |last1=Dehnart |first1=Andy |date=2014-12-22 |work=Reality Blurred |accessdate=2015-04-05 |archive-date=2019-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201160800/https://www.realityblurred.com/realitytv/2014/12/amazing-race-blind-date-major-change/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

本季节目于[[2014年－2015年美国电视网节目表|2015年]]2月15日在[[CBS_(电视网)|CBS]]首播，首播集为时长90分钟的特别集。随后节目改回[[极速前进25|之前一季]]的周五档，于[[北美东部时间|东部时间]]每周五晚8:00播出。本季节目于2015年5月15日完结。<ref name=preview /><ref name=finale/>

本季比赛最终由相亲队伍“[[南加利福尼亞州|南加州]]队”Laura & Tyler获得冠军。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.etonline.com/tv/164656_the_amazing_race_crowns_season_26_winners/|title='The Amazing Race' Crowns Season 26 Winners|work=ETOnline|date=2015-05-15|access-date=2015-05-17|archive-date=2019-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202145412/https://www.etonline.com/tv/164656_the_amazing_race_crowns_season_26_winners|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zap2it.com/blogs/the_amazing_race_season_26_winners_tyler_laura_jelani_jenny_blair_hayley_who_won-2015-05|title='The Amazing Race' Season 26 winners: Laura and Tyler, Jenny and Jelani or Hayley and Blair, who won?|date=2015-05-15|work=Zap2it|access-date=2015-05-17|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619143549/http://www.zap2it.com/blogs/the_amazing_race_season_26_winners_tyler_laura_jelani_jenny_blair_hayley_who_won-2015-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==制作==

===节目开发及录制===
[[File:Castaic_Lake.jpg|thumb]]城外的卡斯泰克湖（{{lang|en|Castaic Lake}}）]]
